OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe rain
OL,6,Fwill clear through the evening,
OL,7,Fleaving a few clear spells, especially
OL,8,Fin the east. However, a small chance
OL,9,Fof isolated showers continues
OL,10,Fovernight. Mild and breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy at first, with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain likely through the
OL,14,Fmorning. Mostly dry by the afternoon,
OL,15,Fthough isolated showers remain
OL,16,Fpossible. Blustery westerly winds
OL,17,Fexpected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
