OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry through this period with
OL,7,Fpatchy cloud and sunny spells, though
OL,8,Fthe odd shower is possible on
OL,9,FSaturday. Breezy on Saturday, easing
OL,10,Fto light by Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
